---
import hero1 from "../../assets/culture/hero-1.png";
import hero2 from "../../assets/culture/hero-2.png";
import hero3 from "../../assets/culture/hero-3.png";
import hero4 from "../../assets/culture/hero-4.png";
---

<section class="px-6 fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 1400ms;">
    <div
        class="bg-neutral-950 grid grid-cols-2 px-6 py-10 gap-y-10 gap-x-6 border border-neutral-800 mt-2"
    >
        <div class="col-span-2 text-[10px]">
            <button class="bg-stone-50 rounded-lg text-neutral-900 px-3 py-2"
                >Company</button
            ><button
                class="border rounded-lg text-stone-50 border-stone-50 px-3 py-2"
                >Culture</button
            >
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-stone-100 text-7xl">
            Locate your uncharted passion <i>here</i>.
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 text-stone-300 text-lg gap-x-6">
            <p>
                We're creating an environment to keep everyone standout with
                their talents and be able to cherish each and every unique
                qualities that we have.
            </p>
            <p>
                Dare to act, own the work, be the truest you. Seizing
                opportunities daily, that’s how we do.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <!-- 1 -->
        <div
            class="col-span-1 rounded-sm p-4 space-y-4 group gradient-border-1 hover:bg-black/16"
        >
            <div class="flex justify-between items-end space-x-2">
                <h5 class="text-2xl text-stone-50">People can Count on Us.</h5>
                <p
                    class="text-[10px] text-neutral-400 group-hover:text-stone-200 border border-neutral-600 group-hover:border-stone-200 rounded-xl px-2 py-1"
                >
                    Commitment
                </p>
            </div>
            <img src={hero1.src} alt="" class="w-full rounded-sm" />
            <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">
                Technologies that integrate, process, analyze, and visualize big
                data for your collective’s solution.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 2 -->
        <div
            class="col-span-1 rounded-sm p-4 space-y-4 group gradient-border-1 hover:bg-black/16"
        >
            <div class="flex justify-between items-end space-x-2">
                <h5 class="text-2xl text-stone-50">
                    Take Risk, Take Ownership.
                </h5>
                <p
                    class="text-[10px] text-neutral-400 group-hover:text-stone-200 border border-neutral-600 group-hover:border-stone-200 rounded-xl px-2 py-1"
                >
                    Courageous
                </p>
            </div>
            <img src={hero2.src} alt="" class="w-full rounded-sm" />
            <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">
                Connect to IoT and AI tools, models, or hardwares for furhterly
                advanced and integrated problem solving.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 3 -->
        <div
            class="col-span-1 rounded-sm p-4 space-y-4 group gradient-border-1 hover:bg-black/16"
        >
            <div class="flex justify-between items-end space-x-2">
                <h5 class="text-2xl text-stone-50">
                    Setting our Priorities Right
                </h5>
                <p
                    class="text-[10px] text-neutral-400 group-hover:text-stone-200 border border-neutral-600 group-hover:border-stone-200 rounded-xl px-2 py-1"
                >
                    Focused
                </p>
            </div>
            <img src={hero3.src} alt="" class="w-full rounded-sm" />
            <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">
                Advanced tools that Braga provides helps to come up with
                analytics that beneficial to tackle various challanges.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 4 -->
        <div
            class="col-span-1 rounded-sm p-4 space-y-4 group gradient-border-1 hover:bg-black/16"
        >
            <div class="flex justify-between items-end space-x-2">
                <h5 class="text-2xl text-stone-50">
                    Be Your True and Honest Self.
                </h5>
                <p
                    class="text-[10px] text-neutral-400 group-hover:text-stone-200 border border-neutral-600 group-hover:border-stone-200 rounded-xl px-2 py-1"
                >
                    Openness
                </p>
            </div>
            <img src={hero4.src} alt="" class="w-full rounded-sm" />
            <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">
                Not bounded by space and time, we help in multiple platforms,
                adapting to different conditions and terrains.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
